    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Available for the discerning driver is a mechanically sound E46 M3, powered by the legendary S54 3.2L inline-six featuring individual throttle bodies and dual-VANOS variable valve timing. This example utilizes the tactile 6-speed Getrag manual transmission and a factory M-Variable limited-slip differential for precise power delivery. The chassis has been proactively addressed with rear subframe reinforcement and refreshed bushings, ensuring the integrity of its McPherson strut front and multi-link rear suspension geometry. Recent preventative maintenance includes a documented valve adjustment and cooling system overhaul. While the aesthetic condition reflects its age through minor road-wear, the drivetrain remains robust and optimized for peak lateral and longitudinal performance.",
